parameters:
Phantom Thief Perno: I'm glad you came. This will be the
location of our final mission.
Clea: I'm glad to see you're doing better than I expected.

Phantom Thief Perno: Hehe, your recent movements weren't
magic, but your own skills, right?

Mage Relm: It seems like you can be a phantom thief even
without magic... However, I understand that Perno's magical
power is quite unstable.

Phantom Thief Perno: That's right. The problem isn't that I
can't use magic, but that it goes out of control.

Phantom Thief Perno: I try to avoid using magic as much as
possible, only using it when absolutely necessary. That's
why infiltration is difficult.

Phantom Thief Perno: It seems that the original Phantom
Thief Perno was a monk here, and he stole the crystal that
the church had hidden.

Monk Sophia: I have heard that there is a crystal that
brings both fortune and corruption to its possessor.

Phantom Thief Perno: This will be the final item to be
returned, known as the Left Eye of Dilei. I'm counting on
your cooperation.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Phoni the Phantom Thief: Are you ready to make the return?

Phantom Thief Perno: There are two gatekeepers... I guess I
have no choice but to use magic here.

Phantom Thief Perno: I'll put the gatekeepers to sleep.
Everyone, be careful not to get involved, okay?

Phantom Thief Perno: Everyone, there's no problem with
this--

Clea: This sensation... It's similar to before... No, even
more than that...

Thief Nora: Hey, I'm feeling sleepy... ugh... *mumble
mumble*

Mage Relm: Ah, I can't resist... My magic power is
completely running wild... and... Ahh...!

Priestess Sophia: Th-this is... resistance... in the end...
ugh

Phantom Thief Perno: Why...! My magic power is completely
going out of control...

Phantom Thief Perno (She really doesn't intend to quit being
a phantom thief)

Phantom Thief Perno: I will definitely come back. I won't
let the help you've given me go to waste.

Phantom Thief Perno: I am Phantom Thief Perno... I will put
an end to Phantom Thief Perno, swearing on the pride of my
family.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Phoni the Phantom Thief: Are you ready to make the return?

Mage Relm: Phew, that was close... It would have been a big
problem if I didn't have this brilliant flash magic!
Priestess Sophia: Hehe, all's well that ends well, isn't it?

Thief Nora: That's right! Even Perno-san is safe. With this,
the mission is complete!

Thief Perno: Finally, it's over... Thinking that way, it
seems like I've lost a bit of strength.

Thief Perno: I'm sorry to always ask, but could you give me
a ride to the campus?

Thief Perno: If the Thief Perno is over, I can also pay you
a reward, you know♪
Clea: Understood, I will definitely escort you home.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Clea (She's sleeping soundly. I wonder if it's because the
magic effect of the Phantom Thief Perno is still in effect?)

Clea (She's sleeping soundly. I wonder if it's because the
magic effect of the Phantom Thief Perno is still in effect?)

Mansion Gatekeeper: I've been ordered not to let anyone
through, so please leave this place immediately.

Mansion Gatekeeper: I've been ordered not to let anyone
through, so please leave this place immediately.

Mansion Gatekeeper: Do you have any business with Lord
Skiros?

Thief Nora: I've come to talk about the collaborator of the
phantom thief.

Mansion Gatekeeper: Huh, so you're the tenth female guest
today.

Mansion Gatekeeper: Ideally, I would turn you away at the
gate, but it's Lord Skiros' orders. You may enter.
Thief Nora: T-Thank you very much!

Mansion Gatekeeper: Wait, the screening is one person at a
time.

Priestess Sophia: May I ask the reason why the women have
come?

Mansion Gatekeeper: Lord Skiros doesn't want to capture the
collaborator of the phantom thief.

Mansion Gatekeeper: It's a strange story, but... it seems
like you really want to meet the collaborator of the phantom
thief.
Mage Relm: Y-Yes, it certainly is a strange story...

Mansion Gatekeeper: I don't know how it got misunderstood,
but there have been rumors circulating that Lord Skiros is
looking for a fiancée.

Mansion Gatekeeper: I am here every day, dealing with self-
proclaimed collaborators of the phantom thief.

Mansion Gatekeeper: Lord Skiros, who wants this to be over
quickly, is a splendid person...

Mansion Gatekeeper: Honestly, he's quite an eccentric
person.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Thief Nora: I was able to withdraw the request from Oros!
Clea: I'm glad that Nora-san is safe.

Thief Nora: They said they want you to come and play again.
It seems that the people from Oros will be issuing a
different request so they won't be troubled.
Clea: If it's resolved safely, let's return today.

Thief Nora (I did something incredible today... Even though
I didn't want to and I should have been scared... My body
still feels hot).

Thief Nora (If I accept the request, I can come back here
again...)
Clea: Are you okay? Your face looks red.
Thief Nora: I-I'm fine! Let's return to our journey!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mansion Gatekeeper: Lord Skiros is currently out. I have
been ordered not to let anyone through.
